author: PowerfulJRE
description:
Katee Sackhoff is an actor known for such roles as Kara "Starbuck" Thrace on "Battlestar Galactica," Bo-Katan Kryze on "The Mandalorian," and Vic Moretti on "Longmire." In addition to her work on-screen, she hosts "The Sackhoff Show" podcast.
